  "stem": "<p>For two acute angles, \u2220Q and \u2220R, cos Q = sin R. The measures, in degrees, of \u2220Q and \u2220R are 2x + 33 and 3x + 7, respectively. What is the value of x?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>5</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p>8</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "c",
      "content": "<p>10</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "d",
      "content": "<p>16</p>"
    }
