    "c"
  ],
  "rationale": "<p>If cos Q = sin R for two acute angles, then Q and R are complementary, i.e., Q + R = 90\u00b0. Substituting, (2x + 33) + (3x + 7) = 90, so 5x + 40 = 90 and x = 10.</p>",
